|---|---|---|
| `apps/app/next.config.ts:25-30` | `withProject` | `lightfast-platform.vercel.app` |
| `apps/app/src/lib/project-urls.ts:7-12` | `withProject` | `lightfast-platform.vercel.app` |
| `apps/platform/src/lib/project-urls.ts:9-12` | `withProject` | `lightfast.ai` ← **the bug** |
